		         ['Barrow-Mound',	'Sea Floor 2',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You are hunched in the cramped spaces underneath the barrow-mounds. The moldering stench of rot is everywhere and the roots of trees occasionally brush your back and obscure your vision.',	'You are standing atop a small, verdant hillock.  Many small grave markers in various states of disrepair are scattered about the area.',	1,	'7D9C62',	'BarrowMound.gif',	20,	20,	20,	20,	204],
		         ['Maglev Tracks',	'Maglev Tracks',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area appears to be some sort of forgotten rail transport. The tracks are in the air on a concrete bridge.',	1,	'44CCCC',	'MaglevTracks.gif',	15,	0,	5,	0,	205],
		         ['Mausoleum',	'Mausoleum',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You are standing inside a small, white-walled building filled with dust and cobwebs. Several moldering bodies are laid in the niches on either side of the room. The faint reek of death is everywhere.',	'This windowless whitewashed building is in a state of mild disrepair. An iron gate swings on rusted hinges in front of the door and the grass around the building has grown wild and long.',	1,	'D8C1BE',	'Mausoleum.gif',	20,	20,	20,	20,	206],
		         ['Birch Meadow',	'Birch Meadow',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area has obviously been left to the wild. The grass here has grown tall and whispers in the breeze.',	1,	'00BB00',	'BirchMeadow.gif',	15,	0,	5,	0,	207],
		         ['Corrupted Meadow',	'Corrupted Meadow',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area has obviously been left to the wild. The grass here seems unusually dark. Cracks have opened in the ground, and the smell of surfer spews out from them.',	1,	'007700',	'Grassland.gif',	15,	0,	5,	0,	208],
		         ['Idyllic Meadow',	'Idyllic Meadow',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area has obviously been left to the wild. The grass here has grown tall and seems to sing in the breeze. ',	1,	'22DD22',	'Grassland.gif',	15,	0,	5,	0,	209],
		         ['Birch Forest',	'Birch Forest',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area is thick with all manner of trees and shrubs.',	1,	'006633',	'Forest.gif',	20,	0,	30,	0,	210],
		         ['Corrupted Forest',	'Corrupted Forest',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area is thick with all manner of trees and shrubs. Limbs seem to reach out towards you, and branches groan in the wind.',	1,	'004400',	'Forest.gif',	20,	0,	30,	0,	211],
		         ['Idyllic Forest',	'Idyllic Forest',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area is thick with all manner of trees and shrubs. Beams of light cut through the trees and illuminate the entire area.',	1,	'228855',	'Forest.gif',	35,	0,	30,	0,	212],
		         ['Treehouse',	'Treehouse',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior of this tree uses an interesting two-level design, with footholds build into the wall for ascent to the second level. ',	'This is a fairly large tree which has been hollowed out. In spite of this, the tree seems to be thriving.',	1,	'E7C6A5',	'Treehouse.gif',	30,	30,	20,	20,	213],
		         ['Corrupted Treehouse',	'Corrupted Treehouse',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior of this tree uses an interesting 2 level design, with skulls embedded into the wall for use as footholds build into the wall for ascent to the second level. ',	'This is a fairly large tree which has been hallowed out. The tree does not seem to have survived this process.',	1,	'C5A483',	'Treehouse.gif',	10,	30,	20,	20,	214],
		         ['Idyllic Treehouse',	'Idyllic Treehouse',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior of this tree uses an interesting 2 level design, with a small ivory ladder for ascent to the second level. ',	'This is a fairly large tree which has been hallowed out. In spite of this, the tree seems to be thriving. Many birds have taken nest in the tree, and occasionally a small woodland creature can be seen running around.',	1,	'FFE8C7',	'Treehouse.gif',	10,	30,	20,	20,	215],
		         ['Corrupted Elder Birch',	'Great Elder Birch',	1,	0,	1,	0,	0,	'This is a grand and open section of the tree, decorated with blood murals on animal hides and sculptures made of bone.',	'This is a gigantic tree with a hollowed inside. It appears to have been turned into some kind of temple.',	1,	'656815',	'Elder_Birch.gif',	15,	25,	10,	15,	216],
		         ['Sanctified Elder Birch',	'Sanctified Elder Birch',	1,	0,	1,	0,	0,	'This is a grand and open section of the tree, decorated with paintings done on animal hides and wooden sculptures.',	'This is a gigantic tree with a hollowed inside. It appears to have been turned into some kind of temple.',	1,	'BAC36A',	'Elder_Birch.gif',	15,	25,	10,	15,	217],
		         ['Great Elder Birch',	'Great Elder Birch',	1,	0,	1,	0,	0,	'This is a grand and open section of the tree, decorated with paintings done on animal hides and wooden sculptures.',	'This is a gigantic tree with a hollowed inside. It appears to have been turned into some kind of temple.',	1,	'98A148',	'Elder_Birch.gif',	15,	25,	10,	15,	218],
		         ['Colonial Bridge',	'Colonial Bridge',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This is a section of a low arching wooden bridge. The dirty water of the river flows beneath you.',	1,	'663300',	'',	10,	0,	10,	0,	219],
		         ['Magi Armory',	'Magi Armory',	1,	1,	1,	1,	0,	'This area is spartan, and what furniture there is here is simple and metal.',	'This is a large, open area. Several metallic bivouacs have been erected around the area.',	1,	'336600',	'Military_Base.gif',	15,	30,	10,	30,	220],
		         ['Colonial Road',	'Colonial Road',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This rough cobblestone road is in ill repair, with frequent chunks of cobble missing.',	1,	'A5A5A5',	'',	10,	0,	10,	0,	221],
		         ['Colonial Park',	'Colonial Park',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This slightly withered park could really do with some maintenance. The gravel path is scattered everywhere, the plant beds are full of weeds and the fountains are broken.',	1,	'00B050',	'',	15,	0,	25,	0,	222],
		         ['Colonial Town Hall',	'Colonial Town Hall',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is part of a large vaulted chamber. The chamber is filled with posh leather seats, and the acoustics of the room are quite grand.  Along the outside of the central vaulting chamber lies many book filled rooms.',	'This is an ornately decorated building, whose appearance suggests some governmental function. Statues of elderly overweight men are scattered infrequentoy between pillars.',	1,	'7F7F7F',	'',	15,	35,	10,	15,	223],
		         ['Caustic Cavern',	'Caustic Cavern',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'Acid drips from the ceiling and lands on the ground in a sickening hiss. It is difficult to breathe, and several half dissolved skeletons are scattered throughout the area.',	'Acid drips from the ceiling and lands on the ground in a sickening hiss. It is difficult to breathe, and several half dissolved skeletons are scattered throughout the area.',	6,	'11aa11',	'',	0,	30,	0,	5,	224],
		         ['Lavaflow',	'Lavaflow',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'A river of molten rock flows through a large crevice in the area. A few pillars of stone seem to be the right distance for hopping across.',	'',	6,	'FF3300',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	225],
		         ['Rotyard',	'Rotyard',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The area is full of several piles of corpses which seem to be resisting the effects of the acid. The stench is horrible.',	'',	6,	'777733',	'',	0,	0,	0,	100,	226],
		         ['Acrid Rampart',	'Acrid Fortress',	1,	1,	1,	1,	1,	'Every inch of the interior is covered in rust, and the horrid air makes you choke. ',	'A large, rusting building stands inside of the cavern. It appears to have once served as a fortress of some kind.',	6,	'A0522D',	'AcridRampart.gif',	20,	20,	20,	20,	227],
		         ['Noxious Tunnel',	'Noxious Tunnel',	0,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'You are standing inside of a mist filled cavern. The air here is virtually unbreathable. You gag and cough as you enter. It obscures the walls, ceiling and limits your ability to see where you\'ve been and where you\'re going.',	'',	6,	'78AB46',	'',	0,	0,	0,	20,	228],
		         ['Dark Cave',	'Dark Cave',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'This is a deep dark cave with many windy tunnels, the sides of which are made of a thick, rock-like substance.  The tunnel has been worn smooth by the frequent passage of something.',	'This is very rough terrain.  Rocks form jagged monoliths and debris. There is a gaping dark hole in the ground here.',	1,	'5C3317',	'DarkCave.gif',	15,	30,	20,	30,	229],
		         ['Dank Cave',	'Dank Cave',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'This is a large dank cave, the sides of which are made of a thick, rock-like substance.  The tunnel has been worn smooth by the frequent passage of something.  The air stinks as though something filthy has lived here.',	'There is a small mound here with an opening.  The grass has been worn to a path leading to the opening.',	1,	'5E2612',	'',	15,	15,	20,	30,	230],
		         ['Colonial Bait Shop',	'Colonial Bait Shop',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is clearly a bait shop of some kind... rotten fishing poles line the walls, and the center is taken up with jars full of dirt.',	'This is a ramshackle shed nearly hidden in undergrowth. A board with a crudely drawn picture of a fishing hook hangs above the entrance.',	1,	'B6DDE8',	'BaitShop.gif',	15,	35,	10,	15,	231],
		         ['Colonial Burlesque House',	'Colonial Burlesque House',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'This is a large room, full of worn out chairs, all pointing towards a central stage. A large rust colored stain is baked into the floor near the exit out.',	'This looks to be an unassuming large mansion, whose facade seems to be in a state of disrepair.',	1,	'FCD5B4',	'BurlesqueHouse.gif',	15,	35,	15,	20,	232],
		         ['Colonial Slum',	'Colonial Slum',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior of the slums looks even worse than the outside, with many patches of wall simply missing, or covered in enough dry rot that it could collapse at any moment.',	'These are a series of run down hovels and shacks, that someone has linked together by means of equally run down looking constructions.',	1,	'FAC090',	'',	15,	40,	10,	45,	233],
		         ['Colonial Inn',	'Colonial Inn',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The upper level of this building is filled entirely with old musty beds, while the lower level is mostly one large room. A fireplace in remarkable good condition is set opposite the main door inside',	'The wooden building is slightly rotted from it\'s proximity to the humid sea air. A sign with a crudely painted picture of a bed hangs over the door.',	1,	'FFC000',	'ColonialInn.gif',	10,	35,	10,	25,	234],
		         ['Colonial Pub',	'Colonial Pub',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'This brightly lit room is full of wobbly tables, broken chairs, and tipped over stools. A long bar is placed along one side of the room.',	'The brightly painted wooden hut is in better repair than most of its neighboring buildings. A brightly painted sign with a picture of booze on it hangs above its door.',	1,	'FFFF00',	'ColonialPub.gif',	15,	35,	15,	25,	235],
		         ['Colonial Foundry',	'Colonial Foundry',	1,	1,	1,	1,	0,	'A giant forge dominates the center of the room, with molten metal constantly flowing in a frighteningly beautiful lava-fall. Around the outside walls are scattered various workbenches for anything you can think of. Piles of empty and rusty bins litter the floor.',	'Great gouts of smoke constantly belch forth from the central chimney of this huge brick building.',	1,	'C00000',	'ColonialFoundry.gif',	5,	30,	10,	20,	236],
		         ['Marketplace',	'Marketplace',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This is a large, open-air marketplace. Several wooden stalls have been set up to display wears and goods.',	1,	'FBA16C',	'Marketplace.gif',	30,	0,	30,	0,	237],
		         ['Apothecary',	'Apothecary',	1,	0,	1,	0,	0,	'The interior of this hut is cluttered with junk. Several types of plants and mushrooms are scattered everywhere, some hanging up to dry, others carelessly thrown on the floor.',	'This is a small, simple hut with several large windows.',	1,	'CD3700',	'Apothecary.gif',	30,	20,	10,	20,	238],
		         ['Bloody Meadow',	'Bloody Meadow',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'The grass here is trampled and bent, in places stained crimson with the blood of fallen soldiers.  The ground, while level and smooth, is pockmarked with artillery craters.',	1,	'00BB00',	'Grassland.gif',	15,	0,	0,	0,	240],
		         ['Temple Wall',	'Temple Wall',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'The stonework base of this wall is as hard and strong as unassailable conviction.  The plaster and woodwork topping the base stretch up into the sky higher than imagination.  You will sooner grasp true wisdom in your hands than you will the delicate tile roofing far above your head.',	0,	'666666',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	241],
		         ['Temple Guard House',	'Temple Guard House',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This stone, plaster, and wood structure stands before you, imposing and resolute.  You almost think you catch a glimpse of what could be sentries watching from inside the tower.',	0,	'333333',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	242],
		         ['Great Southern Gate',	'Great Southern Gate',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'The open archway of this massive gate seemingly stretches from one side of the horizon to the other.  Painted a brilliant red and glowing with an inner light, it almost distracts you from the two huge statues on either side.\r\n\r\nOne statue glares at you, its mouth open and its eyes, almost, following you as you move.  The other statue stares at you as well, its mouth open and its face clenched.',	1,	'FF0000',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	243],
		         ['Bamboo Grove',	'Bamboo Grove',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'Tall and slender, bamboo trees sway gently as a peaceful breeze rustles through.  You can just barely hear the soft call of some unknown bird as you almost lose yourself in contemplative thought.',	1,	'33FF33',	'',	20,	0,	0,	0,	244],
		         ['Serene Path',	'Serene Path',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'A deep feeling of contentment comes over you as you walk along this dirt path.  The stone crunches most agreeably underneath your feet as the sound seems to buoy your spirits.',	1,	'DD9933',	'',	15,	0,	0,	0,	245],
		         ['Serene Grassland',	'Serene Grassland',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'The sward here grows a deep and verdant green.  The blades of grass sigh in the gentle breeze, speaking to you of things thoughtfully remembered.',	1,	'00BB00',	'Grassland.gif',	15,	0,	0,	0,	246],
		         ['Golden Temple',	'Golden Temple',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'Large gilt pillars stretch from the hardwood floors to the carved ceiling.  Small sculptures are nestled into the numerous alcoves, and objects of art adorn the walls.',	'The burnished gold plating of this temple blazes with all the colors of wisdom, peace, and contemplation.  The perimeter walkways gleam with inner tranquility, giving off warm and lustrous light even in the darkest of hours.',	1,	'FFFF00',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	247],
		         ['Golden Temple Entrance',	'Golden Temple Entrance',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'Large gilt pillars stretch from the hardwood floors to the carved ceiling.  Small sculptures are nestled into the numerous alcoves, and objects of art adorn the walls.\r\n\r\nA pair of heavy cypress wood doors lead outside.  Gleaming brass locks and bolts have been thrown open, and appear to never have been used.',	'The burnished gold plating of this temple blazes with all the colors of wisdom, peace, and contemplation.\r\n\r\nBroad, smooth stairs of polished granite lead up to a tall pair of heavy cypress wood doors.  Gleaming brasswork decorates the front panels and edges, and a large ring is set into each center.',	1,	'FFFF00',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	248],
		         ['Tea House',	'Tea House',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'This small room is spartan, nearly austere in its simplicity.  The floor is covered with mats made of woven rushes, giving visitors a comfortable place to sit.  A piece of decorative scrollwork hangs in a recessed alcove, where also stands a thrown pottery vase with a single flower in it.\r\n\r\nIn the center of the room is a small opening in the floor for a hearth.  A bamboo ladle rests on a metal pot that has been set on the hearth.',	'This small hut is simply built.  Walls of cream- colored plaster and hand- polished wood frame the structure.  A small porch stands before the sliding door, giving visitors an ideal place from which to appreciate the small pond that runs alongside the building.',	1,	'996633',	'',	5,	30,	10,	20,	249],
		         ['Nightingale Flooring',	'Nightingale Flooring',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This covered, simple wooden walkway is made of loosely- fitted boards.  Each step you take makes the flooring chirp and sing, as if a songbird were nearby.',	1,	'996666',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	250],
		         ['Jujutsukan',	'Bujutsukan',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'There is a large space, covered in woven mats of reeds, in the center.  Around the periphery, numerous columns support the ceiling and set off private spaces.  This is obviously a training area for some martial discipline.',	'The cedar and pine walls of this imposing building have been polished by the hands of countless students.  Heavy, thick, and strong, these walls are meant to keep secrets in, and interlopers out.',	1,	'FF9933',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	251],
		         ['Kyudokan',	'Bujutsukan Arch',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The floor of this building is made of smooth wood.  The ceiling is high and spacious and there are many practice targets scattered around.  The back wall slides open to reveal an expanse of greensward and even further targets to practice against.',	'The cedar and pine walls of this imposing building have been polished by the hands of countless students.  Heavy, thick, and strong, these walls are meant to keep secrets in, and interlopers out.',	1,	'FF9933',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	252],
		         ['Kenjutsukan',	'Bujutsukan Ken',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The floor of this building is covered with woven mats made of reeds and rushes.  Swords, pikes, and all manner of melee weapons stand neatly in racks against the wall, awaiting use.',	'The cedar and pine walls of this imposing building have been polished by the hands of countless students.  Heavy, thick, and strong, these walls are meant to keep secrets in, and interlopers out.',	1,	'FF9933',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	253],
		         ['Rock Garden',	'Rock Garden',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area is covered in smooth white pebbles that have been raked into a pleasing symmetry.  Small islands of moss- covered rock stand here and there, and in the background are small tree- like shrubs.',	1,	'CCCC99',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	254],
		         ['Quartz House',	'Quartz House',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior of this house is very pleasing to the eye. The quartz which makes up the home is fogged for privacy, and there are several rooms where the water is calm.',	'This is a humble sized house that appears to have been grown out of Quartz.',	5,	'DDFFFF',	'',	10,	25,	10,	20,	255],
		         ['Opal House',	'Opal House',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior of this house is dark and intimidating. There are several jagged corners and dark places.',	'This is a large house that appears to have been grown out of opal.',	5,	'2F4F4F',	'',	10,	15,	10,	40,	256],
		         ['Turquoise House',	'Turquoise House',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior of this house is surprisingly cozy. The waters are calm and there are several rooms.',	'This is a medium sized house that appears to have been grown out of amethyst.',	5,	'9D6B84',	'',	10,	20,	10,	30,	257],
		         ['Kajijo',	'Kajijo',	1,	1,	0,	1,	0,	'The center of this building is dominated by a large forge.  Racks filled with all manner of metal working tools have been carefully placed along the walls.',	'This is a smallish building made mostly of rough- hewn stone set into thick mortar.  Sturdy walls of wood and plaster support a tiled roof with a stone chimney rising out through the center.',	1,	'33CCFF',	'Smithy.gif',	10,	20,	0,	0,	258],
		         ['Ward of Respite',	'Ward of Respite',	1,	0,	1,	0,	0,	'The interior of this building is a pristine white. There are several beds laid out in a circular pattern around a central pillar.',	'This is a small domed building made entirely of white marble.',	1,	'EB5E66',	'WardOfRespite.gif',	20,	30,	20,	20,	259],
		         ['Dark Alehouse',	'Dark Alehouse',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'It has several small tables and chairs as well as a long counter. A blackened torture rack is in the corner.',	'This building has no visible windows but appears to be a bar of some kind.',	1,	'771144',	'Bar.gif',	15,	20,	10,	20,	260],
		         ['Field Hospital',	'Field Hospital',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The floor of this tent has been covered in straw and sawdust, and an unfortunate amount of blood.  Simple cots for the wounded have been pushed up against the tent walls.',	'There is a large, canvas tent structure here, easily able to hold a few dozen people.  Moans from the dead and dying can be heard coming from beyond the opening tent flap.',	1,	'FF3300',	'',	10,	30,	0,	30,	261],
		         ['Mess Hall',	'Mess Hall',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'Two trestle tables run the length of the building.  Plates and utensils are set, enough to serve a small army.  Stoves are spaced down the center of the room, used for cooking and warmth.',	'This simple wooden building is long, with windows done its length.  Metal chimneys poke up through the roof venting smoke, and the pleasant smell of food is in the air.',	1,	'993333',	'',	15,	20,	0,	20,	262],
		         ['Supply Tent',	'Supply Tent',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The inside of this tent is spacious and well organized.  Crates and boxes, filled with untold and uncounted supplies, are carefully stacked everywhere you look.',	'There is a large, canvas tent here, supported at each end by a tall wooden pole.  There is a tent flap on one end you could open and walk through.',	1,	'660099',	'',	15,	25,	0,	15,	263],
		         ['Smithing Tent',	'Smithing Tent',	1,	1,	1,	1,	0,	'A dizzying array of tools and implements are scattered about this tent.  There is a forge in one corner, gun benches in another, and in a third corner on a long table sit some strange glass tubing and beakers.',	'This is a large tent, sturdily built of heaviest canvas and wood.  A metal chimney sticks up through a hole in the roof, smoke puffing up into the sky.',	1,	'33CCFF',	'',	15,	15,	0,	15,	264],
		         ['Barracks Tent',	'Barracks Tent',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'There are a number of cots set about the area.  A small stove is in the center of the tent, giving off a small measure of warmth.  Clothing and random personal items are scattered here and there.',	'There is a small tent here, large enough for four or five people.  In front of the tent flap is a small campfire with a steaming kettle.',	1,	'FFCC66',	'',	15,	15,	0,	15,	265],
		         ['Artillery Tent',	'Artillery Tent',	1,	1,	0,	0,	0,	'This place is obviously intended for making large field artillery pieces.  Winches, smelting cauldrons, and a forge take up most of the area, while metal tools are everywhere.',	'There is a large tent here.  From inside you can hear the sounds of hammering, smithing, and strong language.',	1,	'336600',	'',	15,	15,	0,	15,	266],
		         ['Command Tent',	'Command Tent',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior is dominated by a large wooden table.  It is covered with battle maps, casualty reports, and muster lists. ',	'There is a large tent here, sturdy and strong and capable of holding many inside.  Flags are stuck in the ground, and signaling equipment and horses are nearby.',	1,	'EEEE55',	'',	15,	15,	0,	15,	267],
		         ['Guard Tower',	'Guard Tower',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The tower extends upwards in a spiral staircase along its outer walls. Each floor has 1 room which has been ransacked beyond recognition.',	'This is a single tower made out of stone bricks. Arrow slits have been cut in the walls every 5 feet or so. Patches of green moss have started growing on the masonry.',	1,	'CD853F',	'GuardTower.gif',	15,	15,	10,	10,	268],
		         ['Volcano',	'Volcano',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'Mountains extend up into the sky.  There jagged points  broken and smoking',	6,	'213D30',	'',	20,	0,	30,	0,	269],
