		         ['Chaos Forest',	'Chaos Forest',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area is surrounded in mist and everything in the area is shifting form before your eyes.',	1,	'006633',	'Forest.gif',	20,	0,	30,	0,	337],
		         ['Tainted River',	'Tainted River',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'Shifting liquid rushes past you. Before your eye, it shifts between blood, potion, water and tar. ',	2,	'3333FF',	'River.gif',	0,	0,	0,	0,	338],
		         ['Stygian Foundry',	'Valentines day stall',	1,	1,	0,	1,	0,	'Hundreds - perhaps thousands - of rusting gears and components fill this building. The parts appear to be used in the construction of giant war machines. Huge, menacing devices and forges lie within.',	'The exterior of this building is made of a soot-blackened stone. Hundreds of small chimneys sprout from its tiled roof.',	1,	'660099',	'Stygian_Foundry.gif',	5,	30,	10,	20,	339],
		         ['Heart of Tholaghru',	'Heart of Tholaghru',	0,	1,	0,	0,	0,	'You stand within an enormous chamber, at it\'s centre a gigantic twisted heart beats corruption out through it\'s veins that pierce the walls in several places. A banner has been strung across the room, \"Congratulations Maze Champion\".',	'Looks like you found the centre of the maze. A WINNER IS YOU.\r\n\r\nOh wait, you\'re actually outside the heart chamber. Sorry!',	1,	'993333',	'',	0,	5,	0,	5,	340],
		         ['Ruined Subway',	'Ruined Subway',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a ruined subway tunnel, the concrete is cracked in several places, occasionally whole chunks of the walls or ceiling have collapsed. Everything is covered in dust and there are skeletons everywhere.',	'You are outside the maze.',	1,	'999999',	'Ruins.gif',	0,	100,	0,	100,	341],
		         ['Stone Pillar Top',	'Stone Pillar Top',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You stand upon a great stone pillar top. The air is cold and still. You can see nothing around you, and peering over the edge the pillar appears to disappear off into infinity.',	'You are outside the maze.',	1,	'ADA96',	'',	0,	5,	0,	0,	342],
		         ['Cloud Way',	'Cloud Way',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You are floating in a cylinder of cloud, the air is pregnant with moisture and you are quickly soaked through.',	'You floating above a cloud obscuring some of the maze.',	4,	'FFFFFF',	'',	0,	1,	0,	25,	343],
		         ['Sky Palace',	'Sky Palace',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'An enormous palace extends upwards precariously from it\'s base on top of the pillar, like an upside down pyramid.',	'You are standing outside the maze.',	1,	'5E7D7E',	'Museum.gif',	0,	25,	0,	10,	344],
		         ['Rough Hewn Tunnel',	'Rough Hewn Tunnel',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The area is dark. The floor is covered in loose rocks making for unsteady footing. In places it narrows forcing you to crawl.',	'Vous Aates A  l\'extAcrieur du labyrinthe',	1,	'213D30',	'',	0,	30,	0,	30,	345],
		         ['Doctors Office',	'Doctors Office',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The halls of this building are painted a bland, near-white green. There is a single furnished room, containing a very nice large oak desk, full of draws.',	'If you were in the maze right now, maybe you could get an appointment.',	1,	'FF3300',	'Hospital.gif',	0,	30,	0,	30,	346],
		         ['Gem Mine',	'Gem Mine',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The walls of this cavern are lined with small gems.',	'You are outside the maze.',	1,	'BBFFF',	'',	0,	40,	0,	0,	347],
		         ['Maze Marketplace',	'Maze Marketplace',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a large, indoor marketplace. Several wooden stalls have been set up to display wares and goods. No one appears to be around to take your money.',	'You are outside the maze. A shopping trip would have been really useful right now.',	1,	'FBA16C',	'Marketplace.gif',	0,	50,	0,	5,	348],
		         ['Eternal Soldier Break Room',	'Eternal Soldier Break Room',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You enter a large gym full of training equipment and energy drinks. Posters of Batman, Bruce Lee and other familiar figures adorn the walls.',	'You are outside the maze. Bet you wish you were an ES right now.',	1,	'991111',	'Iron_Fortess.gif',	0,	45,	0,	0,	349],
		         ['Infernal Behemoth Rec Room',	'Infernal Behemoth Rec Room',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This enormous building stinks to high heaven. Various faded and stained sofas have been placed about, along with scarred and broken tables covered in bowls of miscellaneous meat and drinks.',	'You stand outside the maze. A large bouncer blocks the door ensuring you can\'t get back in.',	1,	'AAEE55',	'Bordello.gif',	0,	50,	0,	1,	350],
		         ['Liferaft',	'Liferaft',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This small rubber boat is the only thing keeping you from the corrosive waters that surround you on all sides.',	'You are floating outside the maze.',	1,	'333399',	'ColonialShip.gif',	0,	20,	0,	5,	351],
		         ['Deserted Island',	'Deserted Island',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This small pristine island somehow survives in the sea of corruption.',	'You are STILL standing outside the maze, you fool.',	1,	'FF9933',	'Beach.gif',	0,	15,	0,	25,	352],
		         ['Corruptor Training school',	'Corruptor Training school',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This school has been set up to look like a mixture of board rooms, government offices and newsrooms. Scattered around are pieces of paper with exercises on how to tempt various types of influential persons.',	'You are standing outside the maze, with your nose pressed up against the glass of the building. You can\'t get back in.',	1,	'9933FF',	'Office_Building.gif',	0,	30,	0,	30,	353],
		         ['Maze Entrance',	'Maze Entrance',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'A large tent has been erected around a pair of stone door ways. Above them on a huge banner are the words: Bring me your strong, your brave, your clever, your quick, can you survive The Great Maze of Tholaghru.',	'You stand outside the large tent that forms the entrance to the maze.',	1,	'CC6600',	'CircusCarnivorous.gif',	0,	1,	0,	0,	354],
		         ['Maze Construction Area',	'Maze Construction Area',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You stand in a small room full of strange metal sheets attached to pistons. Someone has scrawled graffiti on the walls depicting squares and cakes, it talks about loss and dishonesty.',	'It looks like something went wrong. You are standing outside an incomplete part of the maze. The walls are barely holding up and a few faded fliers mention this place being off-limits to the public due to safety reasons.',	1,	'999999',	'',	0,	75,	0,	15,	355],
		         ['Inside the hut',	'Inside the hut',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You stand in a room that appears to be completely organic. Warm fetid air pumps in and out as the walls pulse. A dark viscous fluid smelling of putrefaction pumps slowly into pipes ending in sharp needles. ',	'You are standing outside of...something. You\'re not quite sure what this thing is but you sure as hell don\'t want to touch it for any reason.',	4,	'CC99CC',	'Stone_Hut.gif',	15,	20,	10,	20,	356],
		         ['Searing River',	'Searing River',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'A river of boiling oil, emanating oppressive heat. There is a deafening cacophony of bubbling noise and hissing steam coming from the surface.',	2,	'FE642E',	'SearingRiver.gif',	0,	0,	0,	0,	357],
		         ['Hallowed Ground',	'Hallowed Ground',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'The grassy landscape of this area is dotted with small ruins and statues, making it almost seem like a necropolis. The sounds of battle that once marked this land have been replaced by a soft breeze through tall grass.',	1,	'99ff99',	'HallowedGround.gif',	0,	0,	0,	0,	358],
		         ['Fletcher Camp',	'Fletcher Camp',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'It is roomy and brightly lit by dappled sunlight that trickles in through the walls and roof. The walls are lined with well-crafted bows and an eclectic range of hunting trophies, and the furnishings are grown from living trees and shrubs in a manner much like the building itself.',	'It appears at first to be a grove of trees, but upon closer examination they have been carefully tended over many years to form walls and a roof of latticed branches and vines. The building is made entirely of growing things save for a small stone chimney and a few windows of leaded glass.',	1,	'b0b800',	'HuntersLodge.gif',	15,	35,	10,	30,	359],
		         ['Infernal Lodge',	'Infernal Lodge',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The interior of this building is filled with grotesque displays of various beasts (as well as some angels) which have been stuffed and mounted.',	'This building has been constructed from blackened, carbonized stone that has been deeply carved with unintelligible runes.',	1,	'480626',	'InfernalLodge.gif',	15,	35,	25,	20,	360],
		         ['Iron Garrison',	'Iron Garrison',	1,	1,	0,	0,	0,	'This was obviously once (or perhaps still is) used by some sort of hellish military force. There are several racks of various weapons, most of which have decayed and rusted beyond use.',	'This is an imposing structure of irregular angles made from a deep, rusting iron. Several vicious looking spikes are set into the walls, and there appear to be frozen, severed heads stuck to many of them.',	1,	'663333',	'Iron_Garrison.gif',	10,	30,	15,	30,	361],
		         ['Radiant Armory',	'Radiant Armory',	1,	1,	0,	0,	0,	'This building was once used for the manufacture and storage of firearms for an angelic military force. The walls are lined with intricate carvings and there are several racks for weapons storage nearby.',	'This is a towering structure with a glistening sheen, although it was obviously constructed in the distant past. Several imposing statues, all of which seem to be angelic heroes, stand at attention on the ramparts.',	1,	'fff700',	'RadiantArmory.gif',	10,	30,	15,	30,	362],
		         ['Slaughterhouse',	'Slaughterhouse',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The inside of this building is extremely cold. Hundreds of large meathooks hang from the ceiling, and there are several large, blood-stained tables scattered about.',	'This is a large, one-and-a-half storied building constructed of dingy white stone.',	1,	'990066',	'Slaughterhouse.gif',	15,	20,	10,	20,	363],
		         ['Train Station',	'Train Station',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This is a cement platform with several rusting metal benches. A tattered awning which once kept waiting passengers dry, seems unlikely to offer any protection from the elements now.',	1,	'AA22FF',	'TrainStation.gif',	15,	0,	15,	0,	365],
		         ['Skyscraper',	'Office Building',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The building\'s floors are filled with empty, cobweb ridden cubicles. The elevators no longer work.',	'This enormous building is almost a hundred stories tall and is made of glass and steel.',	1,	'84dffc',	'OlympicTower2.gif',	15,	30,	10,	30,	366],
		         ['Mountain Summit',	'Mountain Summit',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This is the snow-capped peak of a tall mountain. The air here is bitterly cold and the wind is constantly blowing. You can see the clouds beneath you from here.',	6,	'f4f6f6',	'MountainSummit.gif',	15,	0,	30,	0,	368],
		         ['Mansion',	'Mansion',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The interior is lavishly decorated. Antiques seem to be found in every corner. Most of the furniture here is made of dark-stained wood and is in good condition. The rooms are very large.',	'This is a very large house with a large, well-kept lawn. The main building has multiple wings.',	1,	'CC9933',	'Mansion.gif',	15,	30,	10,	30,	369],
		         ['Sewer Tunnel',	'Sewer Tunnel',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a grimy, waste-filled sewer tunnel, just barely tall enough for you to stand in. The walls are cylindrical. Everything around you seems to be coated in filth, and the stale, putrid air makes every breath a challenge.',	'',	1,	'ccd7cc',	'',	0,	0,	0,	5,	370],
		         ['Sewer Maintenance Room',	'Maintenance Room',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a maintenance storeroom for the city sewer system, cluttered with broken machinery and other garbage. Empty shelves, stained with paint and fuel, are visible along the back wall.',	'',	1,	'845757',	'SewerMaintenance.gif',	0,	0,	0,	20,	371],
		         ['Sewer Tunnel',	'Sewer Tunnel',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a grimy, waste-filled sewer tunnel, just barely tall enough for you to stand in. The walls are cylindrical. Everything around you seems to be coated in filth, and the stale, putrid air makes every breath a challenge.',	'',	1,	'ccd7cc',	'',	0,	30,	0,	5,	372],
		         ['Sewer Access',	'Sewer Access',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'Above you is a manhole cover which allows a tiny glint of light to shine in from the surface. The walls here are grimy but featureless, and the concrete floor is marked with narrow channels to prevent flooding.',	'',	1,	'ccd7cc',	'SewerAccess.gif',	0,	30,	0,	5,	373],
		         ['Sewage Control Room',	'Sewage Control Room',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a derelict control room for this city district\'s section of the sewer system. It seems it was intended to be controlled remotely, but an array of broken computers are lined up in several rows here. The remote-controlled door that would have sealed this room off is jammed, and as a result a thin layer of muck has spread across all surfaces.',	'',	1,	'989a9a',	'SewageControl.gif',	0,	0,	0,	0,	374],
		         ['Sewer Power Generator',	'Sewer Generating Room',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is one of the power generating rooms for the sewage pumps, dominated by a single power generator. It seems to have suffered a mechanical failure long ago and no longer functions. Broken bits of machinery, perhaps the result of a fruitless attempt to repair it, are scattered about the ground here.',	'',	1,	'FFFFCC',	'SewerPower.gif',	0,	0,	0,	30,	375],
		         ['Flooded Sewer Tunnel',	'Flooded Sewer Tunnel',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'Seawater from an unknown source has entered this area of the sewer tunnels, and the sewage pumps failed to completely clear it out before they ceased functioning. The tunnel around you disappears into the murky, garbage-filled waters here.',	'',	5,	'3333FF',	'FloodedSewer.gif',	0,	0,	0,	0,	376],
		         ['Subterranean Elevator',	'Subterranean Elevator',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a noisy, slow-moving elevator that travels to and from the surface. The sound of the enormous gears moving the elevator is almost deafening, and the doors of the elevator have to be opened and closed by hand.',	'',	1,	'b0b2b2',	'SubElevator.gif',	0,	15,	0,	15,	377],
		         ['Subterranean Railway',	'Subterranean Railway',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is an underground tunnel containing dim lights along smooth concrete walls. At the center of the tunnel is a monorail track that disappears into the darkness ahead of you, but no railway car is visible.',	'',	1,	'b0b2b2',	'SubRailway.gif',	15,	0,	5,	0,	378],
		         ['Subterranean Tunnel',	'Subterranean Tunnel',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'These tunnels are utterly featureless aside from dim lights along the walls. The walls and ceiling are made of reinforced concrete, and a faint musty smell hangs in the air.',	'',	1,	'cccccc',	'',	0,	0,	0,	0,	379],
		         ['Subterranean Welcome Center',	'Subterranean Welcome Center',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You stand in the middle of a clean lobby area with a large reception desk in the middle, with seating areas positioned in the four corners of the lobby. The city coat of arms is printed onto the floor, and a kitschy gift shop is located to the left of the reception desk.',	'',	1,	'6d91ff',	'WelcomeCtr.gif',	0,	0,	0,	0,	380],
		         ['Subterranean Dormitory',	'Subterranean Dormitory',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You stand in a multi-level dormitory complex that manages to fill a large cavern; whether the cavern was a natural construct or something created by man is hard to tell. The hallways are mostly featureless, though the rooms are comfortable and seemingly geared toward long-term habitation.',	'',	1,	'f1c79c',	'Apartment.gif',	0,	25,	0,	35,	381],
		         ['Subterranean Medical Clinic',	'Subterranean Medical Clinic',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is a highly advanced medical clinic, meant to serve the needs of the entire underground population. The numerous hallways leading out of the lobby are lined with operating theatres and consultation rooms, and the walls are dotted with digital signage displays, none of which are functional.',	'',	1,	'f62526',	'Hospital.gif',	0,	30,	0,	20,	382],
		         ['Control Room',	'Control Room',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This is what appears to be some kind of control room, with massive, darkened LCD screens along the walls. There are around a dozen desks set up here facing the main screens of the control room, and all are occupied by non-functional computers. A single analog clock on the wall is stopped at midnight.',	'',	1,	'25f6f6',	'ControlRoom.gif',	0,	0,	0,	0,	383],
		         ['Chateau',	'Chateau',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The interior is lavishly decorated. Antiques seem to be found in every corner. Most of the furniture here is made of dark-stained wood and is in good condition. The rooms are very large.',	'This is a very large house with a large, well-kept lawn. The main building has multiple wings.',	1,	'CC9933',	'Chateau.gif',	15,	30,	10,	30,	384],
		         ['Subterranean Storage Facility',	'Subterranean Storage',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This appears to be a massive, underground warehouse, perhaps the largest single area within this underground complex. Box-laden shelves stretch to the ceiling, almost disappearing in the darkness above. Some boxes are scattered haphazardly about, and you can see a forklift that has crashed into one of the facility walls.',	'',	1,	'0066CC',	'Warehouse.gif',	0,	30,	0,	20,	385],
		         ['Subterranean Shop',	'Subterranean Shop',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You stand in a rather large supermarket that contains numerous foods and other essentials for survival here. The clean tiles and sterile atmosphere would make this supermarket indistinguishable from one above ground, except that the ceiling is made of solid rock.',	'',	1,	'FFFF33',	'Corner_Store.gif',	0,	30,	0,	20,	386],
		         ['Subterranean Lounge',	'Subterranean Lounge',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'This bar was meant to satisfy one\'s needs for socialization and dining, and looks quite luxurious and clean. In one corner, a stage is set up for concerts, and a flyer on the wall advertises musicians you\'ve never heard of.',	'',	1,	'993366',	'Bar.gif',	0,	20,	0,	20,	387],
		         ['Bridge Column',	'Bridge Column',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This is a solitary support column of what was once a suspension bridge. The reinforced concrete here is weather-worn and scorched by fire, and roadway debris hangs haphazardly from the top of the column.',	1,	'CCCCCC',	'BridgeColumn.gif',	10,	0,	10,	0,	388],
		         ['Ruined Bridge',	'Ruined Bridge',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This section of bridge, although largely intact, ends precipitously over water and is fire-scorched. Support cables dangle from what remains of the superstructure.',	1,	'CCCCCC',	'RuinedBridge.jpg',	10,	0,	10,	0,	389],
		         ['Lighthouse',	'Lighthouse',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'The keeper\'s quarters are clean, if small, and have been preserved to reflect living conditions roughly a century ago. The lantern chamber atop the tower contains a huge, elaborate lens made of many pieces of curved glass.',	'This is a rounded tower of whitewashed brick that stands atop a rocky promontory overlooking the sea. It is connected to a simple clapboard house that once housed lighthouse keepers. The lamp is dark.',	1,	'CCCCCC',	'Lighthouse.gif',	10,	20,	10,	20,	390],
		         ['Cobblestone Road',	'Cobblestone Road',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'The path here is made of perfectly smooth, evenly distributed stones that glimmer slightly in the light. Short grass has grown in the dirt between the stones.',	1,	'adafaf',	'CobblestoneRoad.gif',	5,	0,	0,	0,	391],
		         ['Hotel',	'Hotel',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'A humble lobby at the entrance gives way to stairwells and elevators here, both leading to rooms which are simple, spartan and for the most part, identical. You find yourself easily lost in the winding, identical corridors.',	'This is a large, unremarkable building that stands about five stories tall and has a beige facade. Whatever signage there was on the front of the hotel is no longer lit up, and some of the letters are missing.',	1,	'6666FF',	'Hotel.gif',	10,	20,	15,	30,	392],
		         ['Port Facility',	'Port Facility',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This area is a maze of densely stacked shipping containers. The containers are painted in many colors, and a few of them have been broken into.',	1,	'CCCCCC',	'Port.gif',	15,	0,	30,	0,	393],
		         ['Zoo Aviary',	'Zoo Aviary',	1,	0,	0,	0,	1,	'Much of the greenhouse roof has been damaged, allowing rain into part of the exhibit. There are no birds - living or dead - to be found, and the plants under undamaged portions of the roof are dry and dead. There is a gift shop here with a variety of souvenir clothing on display.',	'The cages and animal pits are empty, and bits of trash - handbills, mostly - blow in the wind. There is a large greenhouse with a slanted roof here, which a colorful sign advertises as an exhibition of tropical birds.',	1,	'EE22BB',	'Zoo.gif',	25,	20,	10,	20,	394],
		         ['Augmentation Clinic',	'Augmentation Clinic',	1,	0,	1,	0,	1,	'Several small, private waiting rooms are connected to a series of sterilized surgical suites equipped to install and maintain bionic augmentations. One wing of the building contains a number of comfortable recovery rooms.',	'This is a three-story building with a curved glass facade. It is covered with stylized print murals of attractive men and women performing various intellectual and athletic feats.',	1,	'eac440',	'Augmentation.gif',	15,	25,	10,	30,	395],
		         ['Sacred Columbarium',	'Sacred Columbarium',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'This lush, flowered field is filled with small, domed pavilions of white marble and silvery spires that jut out of the ground and extend skyward. Each pavilion contains an ornate silver urn inscribed with the deeds of a great and ancient hero. ',	1,	'dddddd',	'SacredColumbarium.gif',	80,	0,	5,	0,	396],
		         ['Castle',	'Castle',	1,	0,	1,	1,	0,	'The interior is made of cold grey stone, but is finished in colorful tapestries, imported carpets and lace, and carved wooden furniture of exquisite quality. ',	'It has high stone walls built into the side of the mountain, with battlements manned by many guardsmen. The windows are little more than narrow arrow loops at the lowest level, but grow larger further up the castle walls. ',	1,	'606060',	'Castle.gif',	15,	20,	15,	25,	397],
		         ['Euphoria Asylum ',	'Euphoria Asylum ',	1,	0,	1,	0,	0,	'The inside of this building consists of a single large room. Spread about the area are several beds made of marble that appear surprisingly comfortable despite the material used in their construction. Lining one wall are several cabinets and chests, and a large firepit is centered in the room.',	'The doors to to this large building appear to be made of intricately carved marble. Dominating the front of the building is a large statue of a woman with her arms outstretched in a welcoming gesture. The entire area exudes an aura of peace and tranquility.',	1,	'FF99CC',	'EuphoriaAsylum.gif',	10,	20,	15,	30,	398],
		         ['Skyscraper Interior',	'Skyscraper Interior',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The building\'s floors are filled with empty, cobweb ridden cubicles. The elevators no longer work. Looking through the dusty glass windows gives you a bird\'s-eye view of Laurentia.',	'',	1,	'84dffc',	'OlympicTower2.gif',	0,	30,	0,	30,	400],
		         ['Halloween Costume Shop',	'Halloween Costume Shop',	1,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'The shelves of this dimly lit, cobwebbed shop are filled to bursting with articles of clothing with which to costume oneself as countless fantastic creatures both wondrous and frightful. Mannequins and plastic skeletons glare at you from the fringes of the room, and every so once in a while you think you see one move.',	'This shop has a large glass display filled with mannequins dressed up as all manner of strange and spooky creatures. A row of jack-o-lanterns leads the way to a front door which cackles when approached. ',	1,	'#FF7F5',	'Halloween.gif',	20,	100,	15,	30,	401],
		         ['Frigid Lodestone',	'Frigid Lodestone',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You walk through a cavern of ice, lit from below by a deep red glow. The cavern menaces with stalactites of vicious ice, and the walls are inlaid with corpses frozen in tortuous positions.',	'A ring of huge icicles buried in the earth here encircles a sunken, icy amphitheater with icy benches. Above its center hovers a single, enormous ice crystal that glows a sapphire blue and radiates a deep and abiding cold.',	1,	'77AAEE',	'',	0,	0,	30,	0,	402],
		         ['Glacial Palace',	'Glacial Palace',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'You walk through a cavern of ice, lit from below by a deep red glow. The cavern menaces with stalactites of vicious ice, and the walls are inlaid with corpses frozen in tortuous positions.',	'This area is dominated by an enormous spire that appears to have been grown organically from a single ice crystal. It spreads randomly in many directions and is carved with runes and decorations with a superhuman degree of intricacy, but has no apparent entrance.',	1,	'99FFDC',	'',	0,	0,	30,	0,	403],
		         ['Frozen Highway',	'Frozen Highway',	0,	0,	0,	0,	0,	'',	'The grey pavement here is cracked and frozen. Snow has completely blown over the roadway in places.',	1,	'CCCCFF',	'FrozenHighway.gif',	0,	0,	10,	0,	404],
